I found the likely root cause: `target` and `rel` are in `MORE_ATTRIBUTES`, but `DOMStateBuilder.build()` only uses `DefaultIncludeAttributes.ATTRIBUTES` by default, which currently includes `href` but not the other anchor navigation fields. I’m checking the existing in-progress diffs before patching.

